      "writtenOn": "2017-08-16T00:00:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "how\u0027s this going to work with SPIR-V? My understanding for glsl is that Expressions do not have a Precision associated with them, and it is deduced from the variable that they are stored into.",
